metadata.description:
Welcome to [Peach APE Club](https://peachapeclub.xyz). These tokens grant lifetime membership to our private club as well as access to our futures utilities and benefits. Members are invited to monthly yacht parties and exclusive IRL events.
**Peach APE Club** is the world's first web3 travel booking platform. The NFT is also a key to our Elevated Academy where you can learn about **Travel** , **Credits**, **Investing**, and **Businesses**. This portal is packed with valuable up-to-date information that can help you save money and make smarter financial decisions.
